oading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53366435055_e05ff0379d_c.jpg" alt="DSC08023" width="533" height="800" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC08034" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53366434985/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53366434985_bc51196399_c.jpg" alt="DSC08034" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

